-zbrojna.pl/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=9205:zapomniana-bitwa&catid=116:historia&Itemid=145|publisher=polska-zbrojna.pl|accessdate=10 May 2011|date=26 August 2010|language=Polish}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==Further reading==\n* {{cite book|author=Hans von Ahlfen|year=1977|title=Der Kampf um Schlesien 1944/1945|publisher=Motorbuch Verlag|location=Stuttgart|isbn=978-3-87943-480-0}}\n* {{cite book|author=Eberhard Berndt|chapter=Die K\u00e4mpfe um Bautzen 18. bis 27. April 1945|title=Kriegsschauplatz Sachsen 1945. Daten, Fakten, Hintergr\u00fcnde|location=Altenburg/Leipzig|year=1995}}\n* {{cite book|author=Eberhard Berndt|title=Die K\u00e4mpfe um Wei\u00dfenberg und Bautzen im April 1945|publisher=W\u00f6lfersheim-Berstadt|year=1999|isbn=3-7909-0679-4}}\n* {{cite book|author=Wolfgang Fleischer|year=2004|title=Das Kriegsende in Sachsen 1945|publisher=D\u00f6rfler|isbn=978-3-89555-443-8}}\n* {{cite book|author1=Czes\u0142aw Grzelak |author2=Henryk Sta\u0144czyk |author3=Stefan Zwoli\u0144ski |year=2002|title=Armia Berlinga i \u017bymierskiego (Army of Berling and \u017bymierski)|publisher=Wydawnictwo Neriton|location=Warszawa|isbn=978-83-88973-27-7}}\n* {{cite book|author=Kazimierz Kaczmarek|title=Polacy w bitwie pod Budziszynem (Poles in the Battle of Bautzen)|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=p-ZJAAAAIAAJ|accessdate=11 May 2011|year=1970|publisher=Interpress}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070311005707/http://www.myslpolska.icenter.pl/index.php?menu=historia&nr=2005050114473 Forgotten battles (Polish)]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20060504060303/http://www.wp39.netlook.pl/str/uzup/map/map8.html Map (Polish)]\n\n{{World War II}}\n{{coord missing|Saxony}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Battle Of Bautzen (1945)}}\n[[Category:Conflicts in 1945]]\n[[Category:1945 in Germany]]\n[[Category:Battles involving Poland|Bautzen]]\n[[Category:Poland\u2013Soviet Union relations]]\n[[Category:Bautzen]]\n[[Category:Battles of World War II involving Germany|Bautz