1990)\n* '''Aubl.''' \u2013 [[Jean Baptiste Christophore Fus\u00e9e Aublet]] (1720\u20131778)\n* '''Aubr\u00e9v.''' \u2013 [[Andr\u00e9 Aubr\u00e9ville]] (1897\u20131982)\n* '''Aubriet''' \u2013 [[Claude Aubriet]] (1651\u20131742)\n* '''Aucher''' \u2013 [[Pierre Martin R\u00e9mi Aucher-\u00c9loy]] (1792\u20131838)\n* '''Audib.''' \u2013 [[Urbain Audibert]] (1791\u20131846)\n* '''Audubon''' \u2013 [[John James Audubon]] (1785\u20131851)\n* '''Aug.DC.''' \u2013 [[Richard \u00c9mile Augustin de Candolle]] (1868\u20131920)\n* '''Ausserd.''' \u2013 [[Anton Ausserdorfer]] (1836\u20131885) \n* '''A.Usteri''' \u2013 [[Alfred Usteri]] (1869\u20131948)\n* '''Austin''' \u2013 [[Coe Finch Austin]] (1831\u20131880)\n* '''A.V\u00e1zquez''' \u2013 [[Antonio V\u00e1zquez (botanist)|Antonio V\u00e1zquez]] (born 1961)\n* '''A.V.Bobrov''' \u2013 [[Alexey Vladimir Bobrov]] (born 1969)\n* '''A.V.Duthie''' \u2013 [[Augusta Vera Duthie]] (1881\u20131963)\n* '''Av\u00e9-Lall.''' \u2013 [[Julius L\u00e9opold Eduard Av\u00e9-Lallemant]] (1803\u20131867)\n* '''Aver.''' \u2013 {{ill|Leonid Vladimirovich Averyanov|ru|\u0410\u0432\u0435\u0440\u044c\u044f\u043d\u043e\u0432, \u041b\u0435\u043e\u043d\u0438\u0434 \u0412\u043b\u0430\u0434\u0438\u043c\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447}} (born 1955)\n* '''Averyanova''' \u2013 [[Anna Leonidovna Averyanova]] (born 1981)\n* '''A.V.Roberts''' \u2013 [[Andrew Vaughan Roberts]] (born 1940)\n* '''A.Wall''' \u2013 [[Arnold Wall]] (1869\u20131966)\n* '''A.Wallace''' \u2013 [[Alexander Wallace (botanist)|Alexander Wallace]] (1829\u20131899)\n* '''A.W.Benn.''' \u2013 [[Alfred William Bennett]] (1833\u20131902)\n* '''A.Weber''' \u2013 [[Anton Weber]] (born 1947)\n* '''A.W.Hill''' \u2013 [[Arthur William Hill (botanist)|Arthur William Hill]] (1875\u20131941)\n* '''A.W.Howitt''' \u2013 [[Alfred William Howitt]] (1830\u20131908)\n* '''A.Wigg.''' \u2013 [[Heinrich August Ludwig Wiggers]] (1803\u20131880)\n* '''A.W.Purdie''' \u2013 [[Andrew William Purdie]] (1940\u20131989)\n* '''A.W.Russell''' \u2013 [[Anna Worsley Russell]] (1807\u20131876)\n* '''Axelrod''' \u2013 [[Daniel I. Axelrod]] (1910\u20131998)\n* '''Aymard''' \u2013 {{ill|Gerardo Antonio Aymard Corredor|es}} (born 1959)\n* '''Ayres''' \u2013 [[William Port Ayres]] (1815\u20131875)\n* '''Azara''' \u2013 [[F\u00e9lix de Azara]] (1746\u20131821)\n\n== B\u2014Z ==\n{{List of botanists by author abbreviation TOC}}\nTo find entries for '''B\u2014Z''', use the table of contents above.\n\n{{List of botanists by author abbreviation footer}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:List Of Botanists By Author Abbreviation A}}\n[[Category:Botanists with author abbreviations| ]]\n[[Category:Botanical nomenclature|1]]\n[[Category:Lists of botanists|*]]\n[[Category:Lists of biologists by author abbreviation|Botanists]]\n", "name_user": "Declangi", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eA:Ast: ndash for date range", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_botanists_by_author_abbreviation_(A)"}
{"title_page": "Russ Russell", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2018}}\n{{Use British English|date=April 2018}}\n'''Russ Russell''' is a [[United Kingdom|British]] [[record producer]], [[sound engineer]], mixer, mastering engineer, musician and writer.  He has worked all over the world and now is mostly based at Parlour Studios in Kettering in the UK. He was also the guitarist in the psychedelic band Draw, and now plays in British metal band Absolute Power and cosmic mind metal trio, Reformat.\n\nAlthough working in many different styles of music Russ is now mostly known for his work in rock and metal working with bands such as [[Napalm Death]], [[Dimmu Borgir]], [[At the Gates]], [[The Wildhearts]], [[The Exploited]], [[Evile]], [[The Haunted (Swedish band)|The Haunted]], [[Lock Up (UK band)|Lock Up]], [[Defecation (band)|Defecation]], [[Meathook Seed]], [[The Berzerker]], [[The Rotted]], [[Space Ritual (band)|Space Ritual]], Primitive Graven Image, [[Nuclear (band)|Nuclear]], [[Absolute Power (band)|Absolute Power]], [[Leng Tch'e]], [[Nekkrosis]], [[The Ga Ga's]], [[Sikth]], [[Amorphis]], [[New Model Army (band)|New Model Army]], Shrapnel, Luna Riot, Eradikator, Heretic, Evil Scarecrow,<ref>http://www.pledgemusic.com/projects/evilscarecrowgalactichunt</ref> and many more.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\nLatest interview at RecordProduction.com\n[http://recordproduction.com/blog/2009/10/russ-russell-record-producer-feature-at-parlour-sound-studios-uk/]<br />\nSound on Sound Extreme Production Interview Part 1\n[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2yOEs_whudo] - Part 2 [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=14_ipbRzo6o]\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.myspace.com/russrussell] Russ Russell Myspace\n*[http://www.recordproduction.com/russ-russell-record-producer.html] A feature and video interview at recordproduction.com\n*[http://www.audioauthority.co.uk/]  Audio Authority Management\n*[http://www.parlourstudios.co.uk/  Russ Russell's Recording Studio]\n\n{{Authority